    },
    {
        "Key": 78,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她重重地点了点头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 79,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她回头看了一眼一楼的门，然后抱住了我。又在米拉走出来之前松开了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 80,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "克罗瑞娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_12",
        "zh_CN": "再见，playername。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 81,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "再见，克罗瑞娜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 82,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "回去的路程是妮塔开的车。和队员们挨个通讯报了平安，公司的飞行载具也在附近的机场准备好起飞了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 83,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "起飞，降落。经过游乐场，大门紧闭着，摩天轮隐没在夜色中。回到基地，装着那辆房车的运输机刚刚飞往菲洛索亚。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 84,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嘴角有点痒。伸手摸了摸，血痂便脱落了。露出里面新生的皮肤。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 85,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "回过神来，已经坐在了陶的办公室里。她正忙着自己的事，好像没看见我一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 86,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "陶？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 87,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_04",
        "zh_CN": "嗯？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 88,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我在这儿待了多久了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 89,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_05",
        "zh_CN": "半个小时。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 90,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 91,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_06",
        "zh_CN": "想说就说吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 92,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不知道该怎么说。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 93,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_07",
        "zh_CN": "克罗瑞娜吗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 94,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……你都知道了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 95,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_08",
        "zh_CN": "你快把郁闷两个字写在脸上了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 96,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "克罗瑞娜……挺可怜的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 97,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_09",
        "zh_CN": "嗯。我知道一些。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 98,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我不是她的长辈，没有立场干涉她的教育。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 99,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_10",
        "zh_CN": "而且吉诺拉和世界树正处于对立关系。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 100,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 101,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但我想把她带回来。不需要身份、立场、理由，我就是想把她带回来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 102,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你要的东西，我会再想办法。我保证拿到。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 103,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_11",
        "zh_CN": "想做什么就去做吧，不用考虑我这边。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 104,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这么爽快？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 105,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_12",
        "zh_CN": "有的机会只有一次，比如带她回来。而有的事可以回头再说，比如放在实验室里的东西。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 106,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……谢谢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 107,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_13",
        "zh_CN": "慢着——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 108,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我正要起身，陶从办公桌底下提上来一个密封袋，里面装着一个笔记本。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 109,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_14",
        "zh_CN": "这是从载具驾驶舱回收来的，克罗瑞娜的东西。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 110,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_npc003_15",
        "zh_CN": "顺道还给她吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 111,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "做好了决定。我打算立刻出发。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 112,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "飞行载具正在调试，在房间里准备的时候，我看到了密封袋里，有一张照片从笔记本中散落出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 113,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那是一张合照。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 114,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在零落的焰火里，两个人坐在摩天轮的车厢里。女孩笑得很开心——我从没见她笑得这么开心过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 115,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是我们在摩天轮上的合照——克罗瑞娜把这张照片洗了出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 116,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "打开密封袋，把笔记本和照片拿了出来，在桌上摊开。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 117,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "翻来覆去地看着这张照片。在照片的背后，用笔写着一行字——",
