        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_20",
        "zh_CN": "我还要怎么做呢？我不明白。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 129,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_21",
        "zh_CN": "星期五",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 130,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_22",
        "zh_CN": "小姨说，我的病或许有转机了——她请了世界树的专家来治疗我的病，playername亲自来接我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 131,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_23",
        "zh_CN": "她好像很重视这个名字。我查了一下，还以为是电影里的角色。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 132,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_24",
        "zh_CN": "那些事情挂在同一个人身上简直是在吹牛。难道小姨恋爱了？",
