    },
    {
        "Key": 133,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_25",
        "zh_CN": "真的能治好吗？吉诺拉研究了这么久都没什么实质性的进展，两家公司之间有这么大的差距吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 134,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_26",
        "zh_CN": "过两天playername就会来。那我是不是可以偷懒了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 135,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_27",
        "zh_CN": "星期一",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 136,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_28",
        "zh_CN": "“暂且容许我们消极一下吧。”",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 137,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_29",
        "zh_CN": "听到这句话的时候，像是过电一样，从头顶麻到脚趾尖。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 138,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_30",
        "zh_CN": "被允许的消极……所以人们才会常常叹息吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 139,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_31",
        "zh_CN": "playername……真是个不一样的人。和他在一起的时候，有种奇妙的感觉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 140,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_32",
        "zh_CN": "现在想想，有点失态了。书上说，交浅言深是大忌。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 141,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep7_girl022_33",
        "zh_CN": "可是这种心跳加速、浑身麻麻的感觉是怎么回事？",
        "disable": 0
    },
